fixes log_base :: real and log_x :: real
assumes h0 : "log_base = 2"
and h1 : "log_x = sqrt 2"
shows  "log (8 * log_x) log_base = 7 / 2"
a_0.formal solution:
(* ### Problem

 ### Proof
